  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b90\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Five arrested for stealing fertilizer and selling it at high price",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Five people, including officials of the agricultural association, have been arrested in connection with the sale of fertilizer to another party, which was kept for the farmers of Mahaoya Agricultural Services Department. The Police Media Unit reported that the suspects were arrested yesterday.",
        "A complaint was lodged with the Mahaoya police by an officer of the Agricultural Services Office that the fertilizer packages kept for supply to farmers in the Mahaoya region had been stolen from the Mahaoya Regional Agricultural Services Department.",
        "Following this, on the basis of investigations conducted by the police, five people, including the three leaders of the farmers' association, the secretary and one who assisted them, have been arrested for selling the fertilizer to other parties without giving it to the farmers.",
        "The arrested persons are between the ages of 34 and 40 and belong to Mahaoya area, the police said.",
        "111 packets of 50 kg of fertilizer were sold by the suspects and 277,000 rupees received from the sale were also recovered by the police."
      ],
